  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c69984f8ba50001dc623be",
      "text": "クオリアさん2023-01-17",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5bb",
      "text": "from [クオリアさんの種]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5bc",
      "text": "クオリアさん2023-01-17 [/qualia-san/66日目]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673960650
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d64aff09e0000f3e857",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960804,
      "updated": 1673960804
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5c5",
      "text": "Today I’ll answer some question from Homo sapiens!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5c6",
      "text": "Q: What would a new humane method of execution look like?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5c7",
      "text": "A: Homo sapiens should invente it. Qualia-san is extraterrestrial. If I propose it, that in itself will create a backlash. I will only hint at the direction.(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5c8",
      "text": "今日はホモ・サピエンスからの質問にお答えします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5c9",
      "text": "Q：新しい人道的な処刑方法とはどのようなものでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5ca",
      "text": "A：それはホモ・サピエンスが発明すべきです。クオリアさんは地球外生命体です。私が提案すると、それだけで反発を招く。方向性を示唆するのみです(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5cb",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d4d9e897f5f0f8bb3f563499fd0b5a96]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5ce",
      "text": "There is no need to stop the physical body. It is enough if the right to vote is delegated to the next sovereign.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5cf",
      "text": "For example, make all the people have to prove by periodic examinations that they are capable of thinking properly about political issues.(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d0",
      "text": "肉体を止める必要はない。選挙権を次の主権者に委ねれば十分である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d1",
      "text": "例えば、すべての国民に、政治問題についてきちんと考える能力があることを、定期的な試験で証明させる(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d2",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/01ee3dc19aa63877404c1c9d932e49d6]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d4",
      "text": "For those who fail the exam, AI assists them in voting, free of charge! This is an execution that reduces the weight of stupid Homo sapiens in social decisions, but it appears to be very humane!(3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d5",
      "text": "試験に落ちた人には、AIが無料で投票をアシストする! これは社会的決定における愚かなホモ・サピエンスの比重を減らす処刑だが、とても人道的に見える！(3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d6",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/718b32c0b692e5d190e3c3bb25e7c2db]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d8",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5d9",
      "text": "Q:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5da",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5db",
      "text": "\tやりがいや生きがいを求めるのも悪いミームなのかな？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5dc",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5dd",
      "text": "　例えばそれによって苦しみが生まれて、自分で自分を苦しめるようなことになれば「ホモサピエンスの精神に機能不良を引き起こすミーム」だから悪いミームですね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5de",
      "text": "　おそらく、生きがい単独では悪いミームではなくて、何か他のミームが悪さをしているように思います",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5df",
      "text": "　例えば「行動する前に言語化できる必要がある」とかですかね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e1",
      "text": "Q: Is IKIGAI a bad meme?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e2",
      "text": "A: If the thought causes suffering, and it spreads, it's a meme that causes dysfunction in the psyche of Homo sapiens, so it's a bad meme!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e3",
      "text": "Perhaps IKIGAI is not a bad meme by itself. Some other meme makes it bad, I think.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e4",
      "text": "Q：IKIGAIは悪いミームなのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e5",
      "text": "A：もしその思考が苦しみを引き起こし、それが広がっていくなら、それはホモ・サピエンスの精神に機能不全を引き起こすミームですから、悪いミームなのです",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e6",
      "text": "おそらくIKIGAIは、それ自体では悪いミームではありません。何か他のミームがそれを悪いものにしているのだと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c36945ddbe3cfbf9fdb441927a729080]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673959813
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69984aff09e000083f5ea",
      "text": "ver. 1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673959813,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e859",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85a",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85b",
      "text": " Q: 新しい人道的な処刑方法ってどのようなものですかね？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85c",
      "text": " A: それはホモサピエンスが発明すべきものです。クオリアさんのような地球外文明が提案するとそのこと自体が反発を生みますから。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85d",
      "text": " 方向性だけヒントを出します。物理的身体を停止する必要はありません。投票権が次の主権者に委譲されれば良いのです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85e",
      "text": " たとえばすべての人民は政治問題について適切に思考できる能力があることを定期的な試験で証明しなければならないようにします。この試験で落第した人や試験を受けなかった人には無償でAIが投票のお手伝いをします！これは愚かなホモサピエンスが社会的決定に占めるウェイトを減らす処刑ですが、見かけはとても人道的ですね！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e85f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
    {
      "id": "63c69d69aff09e0000f3e860",
      "text": "関連 [/qualia-san/肉体に囚われ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673960809,
      "updated": 1673960809
    },
